snippet.title: Lesson Learned | Date Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
Lesson Learned will be available on May 29, 2024. 

The full version of the game brings a new tower defense adventure for you and your friends. Journey through a bizarre daydream world in the campaign mode solo or co-op!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1563870/Lesson_Learned/ 
XBOX: https://www.xbox.com/games/store/lesson-learned/9PF0ZLQ09BDD
